{"tid":673727,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大英帝國] 澳洲辦完大英國協運動會 近2百人申請庇護","createTime":"2018-05-22T05:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T06:33:32.000Z","uid":141151,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"800aa99246556ee5bb2ed63715a6713b28599dde","tid":673727,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T05:50:11.000Z","msg":"澳洲辦完大英國協運動會 近2百人申請庇護<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E8%BE%A6%E5%AE%8C%E5%A4%A7%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%8D%94%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E6%9C%83-%E8%BF%912%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E5%BA%87%E8%AD%B7-094100484.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%25AE%258C%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258D%2594%25E9%2581%258B%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%259C%2583-%25E8%25BF%25912%25E7%2599%25BE%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%25BA%2587%25E8%25AD%25B7-094100484.html&d=l5eGLvVAMMxnCWCHCGEdVGowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=9003694a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E8%BE%A6%E5%AE%8C%E5%A4%A7%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%8D%94%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E6%9C%83-%E8%BF%912%E7%99%BE%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E5%BA%87%E8%AD%B7-094100484.html</a><br />\n<br />\n澳洲一名官員今天(21日)表示，上個月在黃金海岸(Gold Coast)舉行的大英國協運動會(Commonwealth Games)，有將近200名選手或隨隊官員已在澳洲申請庇護。<br />\n<br />\n在4月4日至15日比賽進行期間，就有數名非洲與會者逃匿無蹤。<br />\n<br />\n為難民發聲者則指出，上週有數名非洲選手終於露臉，就自己的比賽簽證於本月15日到期之後該如何申請庇護，尋求法律建議。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲內政事務部官員葛萊特里(Malisa Golightly)今天在坎培拉(Canberra)一場國會聽證會上表示，約有205名選手或隨隊人員「現正合法待在國內，因為他們已申請某種形式的簽證」。<br />\n<br />\n葛萊特里說，約有190人「已經申請保護簽證」，另外10至15人則是申請其他形式簽證。<br />\n<br />\n葛萊特里表示，目前所有人都是持臨時性的「過橋簽證」(bridging visas)，等待當局評估他們的申請案，但當局並未指出得花多少時間才能知道申請結果。<br />\n<br />\n葛萊特里另外提到，還有大約50人在比賽簽證到期之後滯留澳洲，至今尚未與當局聯繫，或是申請其他簽證。然而即便他們現在沒有簽證，若符合申請標準，他們依舊可以尋求庇護。<br />\n<br />\n葛萊特里並未說明申請簽證的選手與官員國籍，但先前有報導指出，當中有人是來自喀麥隆、烏干達、盧安達與獅子山共和國等地。"},{"pid":"acabbe53f6b7abe2249bd1d030dc807f05e31ea7","tid":673727,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:00:28.000Z","msg":"Qld本身巳經好撚多非洲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一到節日就成個城市大玩「警察vs黑人」"},{"pid":"644ffe27333a8ca383e2a70d7c2415b7af80a2af","tid":673727,"uid":54959,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:04:28.000Z","msg":"運動難民"},{"pid":"05945c142bfda9ad81cbfe7bccf650f819cb5b85","tid":673727,"uid":129379,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:17:20.000Z","msg":"乜尻嘢係大英國協運動會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明係叫英聯邦運動會"},{"pid":"5a99a95963faf508362d5a6be9986978914fde27","tid":673727,"uid":57787,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05945c142bfda9ad81cbfe7bccf650f819cb5b85","tid":673727,"uid":129379,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T06:17:20.000Z","msg":"乜尻嘢係大英國協運動會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明係叫英聯邦運動會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:14:12.000Z","msg":"台灣新聞，台灣係譯大英國協運動會"},{"pid":"9304798ce45dd5b67e35ee7a15d748af11cc5d0c","tid":673727,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:32:08.000Z","msg":"其實每一屆都係咁，唔知10幾年前曼徹斯特嗰次，淨係一個塞拉利昂都走咗半隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後澳洲電台有個節目俾人估墨爾本嗰屆走幾多人"},{"pid":"6b82befa47af405a68664462c458a93fb21bf171","tid":673727,"uid":132038,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T08:58:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4c3731d364c9bae006050426922da29a8fe468e","tid":673727,"uid":24296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b82befa47af405a68664462c458a93fb21bf171","tid":673727,"uid":132038,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T08:58:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T09:28:16.000Z","msg":"澳洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkg